                        <interp inst="t18680817-709-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted, in November</hi>, 1867, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.*—<hi rend="italic">
